  "title": "昼休みの渚",
  "bondId": "nagisa",
  "bondPointsOnComplete": 20,
  "lines": [
    { "speakerId": "narrator", "text": "渚は廊下の窓際で、スマホを見ながらお弁当を食べていた。画面はコメント欄。", "emotion": "neutral", "preSilence": 0.3 },
    { "speakerId": "nagisa", "text": "……あ。", "emotion": "flat", "preSilence": 0.2 },
    { "speakerId": "nagisa", "text": "邪魔しないでよ、返信中なんだけど。", "emotion": "flat", "preSilence": 0.3 },
    { "speakerId": "narrator", "text": "でも、スマホを伏せた。少しだけ。", "emotion": "neutral", "preSilence": 0.5 },
    { "speakerId": "nagisa", "text": "……まあ、いいけど。隣で食べれば。", "emotion": "flat", "preSilence": 0.4 }
  ]
}
